window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Transported to a fantasy world. Gifted the magic of summoning. A hero born to be a conqueror.</b></p> <p>Jake Anders, the Monster Master, has vanquished the Void King and seized control over his domain. However, new challenges arise: other Travelers have entered this world, all of them as formidable and canny as he, and an ancient malevolent entity of corruption has awakened, seeking to blanket all of existence with its foulness.</p> <p>Jake will need to hone his magic and bind more Monsters to his will if he wishes to protect his new home and the beautiful women who love him.</p>"; 
